OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe families of five people killed in
OL,8,Fthe helicopter crash outside Leicester
OL,9,FCity's King Power Stadium six years
OL,10,Fago have paid tribute to them at the
OL,11,Fopening of the inquest.
OL,13,FAmong those reading tributes were the
OL,14,Frelatives of the club's owner, Vichai
OL,15,FSrivaddhanaprabha, who died in the
OL,16,Fcrash on 27 October 2018. He was
OL,17,Fdescribed by them as a family man who
OL,18,Fwas a "great inspiration".
