OL,7,FAll five people onboard the helicopter
OL,8,Fdied after it crashed and burst into
OL,9,Fflames outside Leicester City's
OL,10,Fstadium after a home game against West
OL,11,FHam United.
OL,13,FDuring the jury inquest, which began
OL,14,Fon Monday 13 January at Leicester City
OL,15,FHall more than six years after the
OL,16,Fcrash, senior coroner Professor
OL,17,FCatherine Mason heard a pen portrait
OL,18,Fwritten by the family of Khun Vichai.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
