OL,7,FIn a tribute read to the court by
OL,8,Ffamily barrister Philip Shepherd KC,
OL,9,Fthe relatives said: "Khun Vichai was
OL,10,Fthe leader of our family, a caring and
OL,11,Fdevoted husband, father, uncle and
OL,12,Fgrandfather.
OL,14,F"We feel the loss of him as much today
OL,15,Fas we have ever done. He was a good
OL,16,Fman with a good heart.
OL,18,F"He was a great inspiration to us all
OL,19,Fand we all loved him very much.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
