OL,7,F"It's impossible to put Khun Vichai
OL,8,Finto words. He possessed all of the
OL,9,Fbest qualities.
OL,11,F"He was adored by everyone for his
OL,12,Fkind spirit, generosity, charm, sense
OL,13,Fof humour and intellect."
OL,15,FThe statement added: "Many will
OL,16,Fremember Khun Vichai as the chairman
OL,17,Fof Leicester City Football Club. When
OL,18,Fhe bought the club in 2010, it was
OL,19,Flanguishing in the Championship.
