OL,7,F"Khun Vichai had a vision to put the
OL,8,Fclub in the Premier League. He wanted
OL,9,Fto build the club up, not just run it.
OL,11,F"With his support and commitment the
OL,12,Fteam won the Premier League in 2016 `
OL,13,Fin only their second year in the
OL,14,Fdivision.
OL,16,F"We miss him every day. The pain his
OL,17,Fdeath caused and continues to cause
OL,18,Four family is immeasurable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
