OL,7,F"We continue to struggle every day
OL,8,Fwith our grief. He was a phenomenon.
OL,9,FHe was one of a kind."
OL,11,FThe inquest, which is expected to last
OL,12,Fbetween two and three weeks, is also
OL,13,Flooking into the deaths of the pilot
OL,14,FEric Swaffer and his partner, Izabela
OL,15,FLechowicz, as well as passengers
OL,16,FNusara Suknamai and Kaveporn Punpare,
OL,17,Fwho were all killed in the crash.
