OL,7,FKate Lechowicz, Ms Lechowicz's sister,
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to her as an
OL,9,F"extraordinary individual" who shared
OL,10,Fher love of aviation with her partner.
OL,12,FIn a statement read to the inquest,
OL,13,Fshe said: "She was an extraordinary
OL,14,Findividual, she exuded a passion for
OL,15,Flife, but above all she was a
OL,16,Fdedicated pilot.
OL,18,F"She had extensive global flying
OL,19,Fexperience. She was the type of person
OL,20,Fwho accomplished her task with grace
OL,21,Fand efficiency."
