OL,7,FTributes were also paid to passenger
OL,8,FKaveporn Punpare, who had a young
OL,9,Fdaughter and was one of several
OL,10,Fbutlers employed by Vichai
OL,11,FSrivaddhanaprabha.
OL,13,FA statement prepared for the inquest
OL,14,Fby his wife said the former fitness
OL,15,Finstructor had initially worked for
OL,16,FKhun Vichai as an assistant butler who
OL,17,Faccompanied family members on trips,
OL,18,Fbut was promoted in 2015.
