OL,7,FShe said her husband would be loved
OL,8,Fand missed by his family each and
OL,9,Fevery day.
OL,11,FFormer Miss Thailand contestant Nusara
OL,12,FSuknamai, also a passenger when the
OL,13,Fhelicopter crashed and caught fire,
OL,14,Fwas described at the inquest as a
OL,15,F"pillar" of her family, who said in a
OL,16,Fstatement prepared by a lawyer: "This
OL,17,Fis the greatest loss for the family.
OL,18,FWe will never forget it."
